Ё̀  ->  Ё, # but they will be soon (трё̀хсо́тый).

ё́  ->  ё, # Redundant primary stress mark. Could be used to mark where Russians 
Ё́  ->  Ё  # are more likely to write ё instead of е (e.g. узнаёт). However, this
